reviews.review_text:
Wonderful Source, but not perfect If you have been seeing my posts in the forums, you should know that I am one of those people who are all about perfection. As for this show the sound quality is OK, but for an audience recording it could be better. I also noticed a few errors in the recording (tape cuts).
For a '90s show I am impressed with the performance they gave this night. I would recommend this to those of you who like '90s shows with ENERGY!
